            "action_name": {
              "value": "Fell Necromancy"
            },
            "action_description": {
              "value": "Gremorly targets one creature he can see within 60 feet of himself. The target must make a DC 16 Constitution saving throw, taking 61 (7d8 + 30) necrotic damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. In addition, Gremorly regains 9 (2d8) hit points."
            },
